      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "ph4kzyzgg",
        "uid": "125206"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t连国人降低刑事责任年龄都还没有实施，人的都不能得到保护，何况动物呢？\t\t</div>",
